Installing IBM Installation Manager 1.9.3.2
Steps
1.	Create a directory to extract the binary for IBM Installation Manager
mkdir /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/IM
2.	Extract IBM Installation Manager
unzip agent.installer.linux.gtk.x86_64_1.9.3002.20250425_1344.zip -d /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/IM
3.	Install IBM Installation Manager in Silent Mode
/home/cpeadmin/Softwares/IM/installc -silent -acceptLicense -installationDirectory /opt/IBM/InstallationManager -accessRights nonAdmin
 
4.	[Optional] Check for installed packages
/opt/IBM/InstallationManager/eclipse/tools/imcl listInstalledPackages
 
5.	[Optional] Check Installation Manager version
/opt/IBM/InstallationManager/eclipse/tools/imcl -version

 

Installing IBM WebSphere Application Server 9.0.5.25
Steps
1.	Create directories to extract the binaries for IBM WAS and Fix Pack 
mkdir -p /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/WAS/nd
mkdir -p /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/WAS/fp25
mkdir /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/java35
mkdir /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/java55
2.	Unzip the binaries
unzip was.repo.90501.nd.zip -d /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/WAS/nd
unzip 9.0.5-WS-WAS-FP025.zip -d /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/WAS/fp25
unzip ibm-java-sdk-8.0-8.35-linux-x64-installmgr.zip -d /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/java35
unzip ibm-java-sdk-8.0-8.55-linux-x64-installmgr.zip -d /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/java55
3.	Check for packages in repository config
/opt/IBM/InstallationManager/eclipse/tools/imcl listAvailablePackages -repositories /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/WAS/nd/repository.config
/opt/IBM/InstallationManager/eclipse/tools/imcl listAvailablePackages -repositories /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/WAS/fp25/repository.config
/opt/IBM/InstallationManager/eclipse/tools/imcl listAvailablePackages -repositories /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/java35/repository.config
/opt/IBM/InstallationManager/eclipse/tools/imcl listAvailablePackages -repositories /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/java55/repository.config

 
4.	Install WAS with IBM Java patch level 35.
/opt/IBM/InstallationManager/eclipse/tools/imcl install \
com.ibm.websphere.ND.v90_9.0.5001.20190828_0616 \
com.ibm.java.jdk.v8_8.0.8035.20241125_0150 \
-accessRights nonAdmin \
-acceptLicense \
-showProgress \
-repositories /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/WAS/nd/repository.config,/home/cpeadmin/Softwares/java35/repository.config \
-installationDirectory /opt/IBM/WebSphere/AppServer \
-sharedResourcesDirectory /opt/IBM/IMShared \
-record /home/cpeadmin/Softwares/install_was.xml
  

5.	[Optional] View install_was.xml contents
